          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The primary 6Li beam was accelerated via the K150",
                "Cyclotron to an energy of 9.9MeV/u and transported to",
                "the cryogenic gas target located at the entrance of",
                "Momentum Achromat Recoil Spectrometer (MARS) . The",
                "secondary 8B beam was produced in-flight using the",
                "6Li(3He,n) 8B reaction. The gas-cell target was",
                "filled with 3He at a pressure of 800 Torr and",
                "temperature of 77 K. A 97%- pure 5.1MeV/u 8B beam of",
                "103pps was produced with an energy spread of 1.2 MeV.",
                "Secondary beam was analyzed using MARS spectrometer."
              ]
            }
          ],
